Activity Summary: Type of compound activity based on both the PPARg antagonist mode screen and the cell viability counter screens.
Ratio Activity: Type of compound activity in the ratio readout of the PPARg antagonist mode screen.
Ratio Potency (uM): The concentration of sample yielding half-maximal inhibition in the ratio readout of the PPARg antagonist mode screen.
Ratio Efficacy (%): Percent inhibition in the ratio readout of the PPARg antagonist mode screen.
530 nm Activity: Type of compound activity in the 530 nm readout of the PPARg antagonist mode screen.
530 nm Potency (uM): The concentration of sample yielding half-maximal inhibition in the 530 nm readout of the PPARg antagonist mode screen.
530 nm Efficacy (%): Percent inhibition in the 530 nm readout of the PPARg antagonist mode screen.
460 nm Activity: Type of compound activity in the 460 nm readout of the PPARg antagonist mode screen.
460 nm Potency (uM): The concentration of sample yielding half-maximal inhibition in the 460 nm readout of the PPARg antagonist mode screen.
460 nm Efficacy (%): Percent inhibition in the 460 nm readout of the PPARg antagonist mode screen.
Viability Activity: Type of compound activity in the cell viability counter screens.
Viability Potency (uM): The concentration of sample yielding half-maximal inhibition in the cell viability counter screen.
Viability Efficacy (%): Percent inhibition in the cell viability counter screen.
